text: The Conoco-Phillips Building is a 22-story, office building. Construction began in 1981 and completed in 1983 as the ARCO Building. It is at 700 G Street in downtown Anchorage, Alaska and is the tallest building in both Anchorage and the state of Alaska.Buildings 1981: 106. ==References== Category:Anchorage, Alaska Category:Buildings and structures in the United States
title: Conoco-Phillips Building
